reviewText: No monsters for Santo to fight in this one, just bad guys exploiting Mexican workers as slaves or something. Not too bad compared to other Santo movies, but ultimately a snoozer. For hardcore Santo fans or completists.

I RECIEVED MY DVDS OF EL SANTO MOVIES,THEY WERE EXCELLENT,PICTURE QUALTING.THE MOVIES SANTO EN LA FRONTERA DEL TERROR.I ENOYED THE BLACK AND WHITE AS WELL AS THE COLORED MOVIES,REMINDS ME,WHEN I USE TO SEE THIS MOVIES AT THE DRIVE-IN.
